import numpy as np
from scipy.io import wavfile
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


from pynq import Overlay
from pynq.lib.audio import AudioADAU1761     # to interact with audio codec controller

class MyAudioOverlay(Overlay):
    def __init__(self, bitfile_name="audio_test_v1.bit"):
        super().__init__(bitfile_name)
        
        # IP-Beschreibung aus dem Overlay holen
        audio_description = self.ip_dict['audio_codec_ctrl_0']
        
        # Audioklasse mit Beschreibung initialisieren
        self.audio = AudioADAU1761(audio_description)
        # I2C-Index manuell setzen (wird von libaudio erwartet)
        self.audio.iic_index = 1  # Für PYNQ-Z2: PS-I2C Controller 1
        self.audio.sample_rate = 48000
        self.audio.uio_index = 0
